text: Alida Dóra Gazsó (born 18 April 2000) is a Hungarian sprint canoeist.Profile She won a medal at the 2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships.2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships results ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian female canoeists Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in kayak Category:Canoeists from Budapest
